findings.title: Out of gas exception if there will be a long excluded addresses list
findings.description: The function includeInReward() uses a loop to find and remove addresses from the _excluded list. If the excluded addresses list is too long, it may cause an OUT_OF_GAS exception.

findings.title: OUT_OF_GAS exception if there will be a long sell history list
findings.description: The function _transfer() uses the loop for calculating buyback amount if _isAutoBuyBack set true. It also could be aborted with OUT OF GAS exception if there will be a long sell history list.
